text: Gert Port (born 23 July 1968) is an Austrian rower. He competed in the men's quadruple sculls event at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1968 births Category:Living people Category:Austrian male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Austria Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Klagenfurt
